		height: 430px;
		right: 540px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		z-index: 1;
	}
	.helplist:before {
		background: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.169);
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		width: 520px;
		height: 320px;
		top: -40px;
		left: -40px;
	}
}

</style>